To enable encryption on devices running Android KitKat or Jelly Bean, plug the phone or tablet into charge.

Make sure the device remains connected to the power cable throughout. 

Go to Setting, Security and select Screen Lock. 

Choose a PIN or password and follow the steps. 

Select the Encrypt option when prompted.

